snippet.title: PARADISE ® | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Add us to your Wishlist:
🎮 STEAM・https://store.steampowered.com/app/3281420/Paradise/

PARADISE is a life simulation game with limitless possibilities. 
Play with your friends, engage in shootouts, race cars, complete daily missions, and reach the apex of life. Earn money and buy what you want, from real estate to fancy clothes.
Endless World, Endless Play.

🌏 Website・https://paradisevs.com/
🌐 (X) Twitter・https://x.com/paradisevscom

Song: Busy Earnin’
Artist: Jungle
Written by: Joshua Lloyd-Watson, Tom McFarland
Published by: Universal Music Publishing Group on behalf of Beggars Music
Courtesy of: XL Recordings

Ultra Games Limited and Paradise are independent entities and are not affiliated, associated, partnered with, or endorsed by Epic Games. The game is available on the Epic Games Store.
